role_description: An Ansible role that sets up File Browser, a web GUI for managing your file systems, on nearly any platform
role_description_full_overview: [File Browser](https://filebrowser.org/) is a tool that lets you browse and edit files on any mounting point in the operating system.
role_description_alt: This repository is the home of an Ansible role that sets up File Browser, a web GUI for managing your file systems, on nearly any platform.
